PrecisAmendments to Order in Council P.C. 1995-1/1404 which revise some of the Terms and Conditions of the SPECIALIZED COUNSELLING ASSISTANCE GRANT PROGRAM, extend the deadline for the receipt of applications to March 31, 1997, and extend the program termination date to September 30, 1997.
